OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F16,000 firms go bust owing 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fmillions in Covid loans    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More than 16,000 businesses which took 
OL,6, out a type of government-backed Covid  
OL,7, loan have gone bust without paying the 
OL,8, money back, the BBC has found.         
OL,10,FHundreds of directors, who got loans   
OL,11,Fthey were not entitled to, have also   
OL,12,Fbeen disqualified.                     
OL,14,FThe cost to the taxpayer of these      
OL,15,Finsolvencies could be as much as #500m,
OL,16,Fand is likely to grow as more companies
OL,17,Fgo under.                              
OL,19,FQuestions are now being asked about    
OL,20,Fwhat is being done to recoup the money.
